The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 54

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

It's House 1 versus House 2. Whoever scores the highest points, wins extra cash off their reserve price come auction day. With only days to completely renovate and decorate two houses, have our teams bitten off more than they can chew?
